=======gpg 错误 ========
GPG error: http://us-east-1.ec2.archive.ubuntu.com precise-updates Release: The following signatures were invalid: BADSIG xxxxxxxxxxx Ubuntu Archive Automatic Signing Key <ftpmaster@ubuntu.com>
解决办法：apt-key adv --keyserver keyserver.ubuntu.com --recv-keys xxxxxxxxxx

======禁止ipb6==========
修改/etc/default/grub：GRUB_CMDLINE_LINUX="ipv6.disable=1"
运行：update-grub

